A small chunk of what is my year end review for 2022. 
Took a small break off the bike to focus on my wedding at the beginning of the year and with that came a lot of catching up to do. All in all I am extremely happy with where I stand with BMX and my progression as a whole— mentally, physically and emotionally! Thank you to everyone who believes in me and supports me and most importantly thank you God for this amazing talent I have been gifted with!! 2023, IM READY FOR YOU! 💪🏼😘🚲 HAPPY NEW YEAR everyone! ❤️ 
#newyearseve
